16
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:44,633
<i>And I built their monstrous dwellings... </i>

17
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:46,677
<i>... caskets for their secrets. </i>

18
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:50,196
<i>Mothers. Stepmothers that</i>
<i>do not give birth to life. </i>

19
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:54,478
<i>Sisters. Mistresses of</i>
<i>the horrors of humanity. </i>

20
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:04,990
<i>Men, mistaken, call them with</i>
<i>one terrible name. </i>

21
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:09,233
